description: Seeks to track the performance of Bloomberg Global Aggregate ex-USD Float Adjusted RIC Capped Index (CAD Hedged) to the extent possible and before fees and expenses. Invests primarily in the U.S.-domiciled Vanguard Total International Bond Market ETF. U.S. dollar exposure is hedged to the Canadian dollar. Employs a passively managed, index-sampling strategy to gain exposure to major bond markets outside of the U.S.
name: Vanguard Global ex-U.S. Aggregate Bond Index ETF (CAD-hedged)
